    dc:description "FIGURES 11 ­ 22. Orizabus dechambrei Morón, Tapia and Aragón, sp. nov. 11 ­ Male head, dorsal view; 12 ­ Holotype head and pronotum, lateral view; 13 ­ Paratype ibid; 14 ­ Male foretibia, dorsal view; 15 ­ Female foretibia, dorsal view; 16 ­ Male hindtibia, lateral view; 17 ­ Allotype head and pronotum, lateral view; 18 ­ Holotype clypeal carina, frontal view; 19 ­ Paratype clypeal carina; 20 ­ Parameres, distal view; 21 ­ Male genital capsule, lateral view; 22 ­ Female genital plates, ventral view. Scale bar 1 mm." ;
